### Expressions API — 表达式校验与求值

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!"
}

###

### 1. 校验合法表达式
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/expressions/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "expression": "form.amount >= 1000 && form.status == 'approved'"
}

###

### 2. 校验包含危险模式的表达式（应返回错误）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/expressions/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "expression": "eval('malicious') || form.amount > 0"
}

###

### 3. 表达式求值 — 条件判断（返回 bool）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/expressions/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "expression": "form.amount >= 1000 && form.status == 'approved'",
  "record": {
    "form.amount": "1500",
    "form.status": "approved"
  },
  "user": null,
  "page": null
}

###

### 4. 表达式求值 — contains 函数
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/expressions/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "expression": "form.department.contains('技术')",
  "record": {
    "form.department": "技术部"
  },
  "user": null,
  "page": null
}

###

### 5. 获取表达式中的变量列表（validate 接口返回 variables 字段）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/expressions/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "expression": "form.amount >= user.level && page.mode == 'edit'"
}
